(1, 'SunShine', 'div样式在IE下margin:0 auto不居中多种解决方法  ', '<ul class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><h3 style="line-height: 28.7999992370605px; margin: 15px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;">正常情况下需要将div居中显示时，使用Css样式:margin:0&nbsp;auto即可，但有时使用margin:0&nbsp;auto后在FF、Chrome里能居中，而在IE678里不居中的现象。</h3></li><li><p style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 12.5px;">正常情况下需要将div居中显示时，使用Css样式:<strong style="line-height: 21.875px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">margin:0 auto</strong>即可，但有时使用margin:0 auto后在FF、Chrome里能居中，而在IE678里不居中的现象。</p><p style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 12.5px;">如下代码:<br style="line-height: 21.875px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">XML/HTML Code</span>&nbsp;<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; cursor: pointer;">复制内容到剪贴板</span></p><ol style="line-height: 22.5px; margin: 10px 20px; padding: 0px;" class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&lt;</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">style</span>&nbsp;<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">type</span>=<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&quot;text/css&quot;</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&gt;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></li><li><p>#con{width:980px;martin:0&nbsp;auto;}&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></li><li><p><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&lt;/</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">style</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&gt;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></li><li><p><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&lt;</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">div</span>&nbsp;<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">id</span>=<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&quot;con&quot;</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&gt;</span>margin:&nbsp;0&nbsp;auto&nbsp;内容居中显示<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&lt;/</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">div</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&gt;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></li></ol><h3 style="line-height: 28.7999992370605px; margin: 15px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;"><br style="line-height: 28px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"/>解决方法一</h3><p style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 12.5px;">可以是对网页主体&lt;body&gt;声明文本居中，即body{text-align:center}<br style="line-height: 21.875px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"/>即:<br style="line-height: 21.875px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">XML/HTML Code</span>&nbsp;<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; cursor: pointer;">复制内容到剪贴板</span></p><ol style="line-height: 22.5px; margin: 10px 20px; padding: 0px;" class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&lt;</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">style</span>&nbsp;<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">type</span>=<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&quot;text/css&quot;</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&gt;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></li><li><p>body{text-align:center}&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></li><li><p>#con{width:980px;martin:0&nbsp;auto;}&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></li><li><p><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&lt;/</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">style</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&gt;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></li><li><p><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&lt;</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">div</span>&nbsp;<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">id</span>=<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&quot;con&quot;</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&gt;</span>margin:&nbsp;0&nbsp;auto&nbsp;内容居中显示<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&lt;/</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">div</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&gt;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></li></ol><h3 style="line-height: 28.7999992370605px; margin: 15px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;"><br style="line-height: 28px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"/>解决方法二</h3><p style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 12.5px;">其实和解决方法一差不多，只是在要居中的div外层添加多一个div,并使其居中<br style="line-height: 21.875px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"/>即：<br style="line-height: 21.875px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">XML/HTML Code</span>&nbsp;<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; cursor: pointer;">复制内容到剪贴板</span></p><ol style="line-height: 22.5px; margin: 10px 20px; padding: 0px;" class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&lt;</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">style</span>&nbsp;<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">type</span>=<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&quot;text/css&quot;</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&gt;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></li><li><p>#con{width:980px;martin:0&nbsp;auto;}&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></li><li><p><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&lt;/</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">style</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&gt;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></li><li><p><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&lt;</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">div</span>&nbsp;<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">style</span>=“text-align:center”<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&gt;</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&lt;</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">div</span>&nbsp;<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">id</span>=<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&quot;con&quot;</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&gt;</span>margin:&nbsp;0&nbsp;auto&nbsp;内容居中显示<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&lt;/</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">div</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&gt;</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&lt;/</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">div</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&gt;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></li></ol><h3 style="line-height: 28.7999992370605px; margin: 15px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;">解决方法三</h3><p style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 12.5px;">出现这个现象的原因在于文档的DTD声明；<br style="line-height: 21.875px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"/>修改DTD为</p><p><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">XML/HTML Code</span>&nbsp;<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; cursor: pointer;">复制内容到剪贴板</span></p><ol style="line-height: 22.5px; margin: 10px 20px; padding: 0px;" class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p>&lt;!DOCTYPE&nbsp;html&nbsp;PUBLIC&nbsp;&quot;-//W3C//DTD&nbsp;XHTML&nbsp;1.0&nbsp;Transitional//EN&quot;&nbsp;&quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd&quot;<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">&gt;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></li></ol></li></ul><p><br/></p>', 3, 1, 0, '2015-04-13'),
(4, 'SunShine', 'css中的expression', '<p>以前都没有看到过这个属性，只是在一片大牛的博客中看到，之后再进行百度了一下，原来javascript和css还可以进行这样的结合，顿时长知识了，但是虽然这种表达式看起来很牛逼，但是好像不推荐使用，因为expression对浏览器资源要求过高。</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;expression用来把css和javascript表达式结合起来，也就是css后面也可以加一段javascript的表达式，比如举个例子：</p><p>#head{<br/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;height:expression(this.scrollHeight&gt;200?&quot;200px&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;);</p><p>}</p><p><br/></p><p>现在感觉css还是很强大的。</p><p>详细使用可以参考http://www.cnblogs.com/rubylouvre/archive/2009/07/29/1534330.html</p>', 3, 1, 1, '2015-04-19'),
(5, 'SunShine', '关于thinkphp数据库的配置问题', '<p style="text-align: left;">一直以来都是用的是thinkphp3.12版本，因为视频看的就是就是这个版本，原先看到官网上出了3.2.3的,也尝试过用过，但是由于引入了命名空间，而且有很多关于路径的问题，所以一直也没有敢用。但是这一次是真的想看看两者的区别了</p><p><br style="text-align: left;"/></p><p style="text-align: left;">就关于数据库配置文件的放置问题，也是纠结了好久，以前的做法是在和入口文件的同级目录下新建一个公共的配置文件，暂时取名为$config.inc.php,然后再里面加上数据库的配置，最后在模块的配置目录上引入该配置就行，比如，在home目录下的config目录下的config.php中，就可以写成这种形式</p><p style="text-align: left;">&lt;?php</p><p style="text-align: left;">$program_config = require(&#39;./config.inc.php&#39;);</p><p style="text-align: left;">$configinc = array(</p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="white-space:pre">		</span>//&#39;配置项&#39;=&gt;&#39;配置值&#39;</p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="white-space:pre">		</span>&#39;TMPL_PARSE_STRING&#39; =&gt; array(</p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="white-space:pre">			</span>&#39;__PUBLIC__&#39; =&gt; &#39;/xinxi/Admin/Public&#39;,</p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="white-space:pre">			</span>&#39;__APP__&#39;=&gt;&#39;/xinxi/admin.php&#39;,</p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="white-space:pre">			</span>&#39;__UPLOADS__&#39;=&gt;&#39;/xinxi/Uploads&#39;,</p><p><span style="white-space:pre">			</span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="white-space:pre">		</span>)</p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="white-space:pre">	</span>);</p><p style="text-align: left;">return array_merge( $program_config,$configinc);</p><p style="text-align: left;">?&gt;</p><p style="text-align: left;">但是由于thinkphp3.2以后，目录的层次结构更加复杂了，所以我就想尝试一种新的写法，终于在某个博客上看到了，也就是thinkphp的/Application/Common/config/config中配置数据库的配置文件，这样的话，前台和后台的文档都可以使用这份配置文件，当然了，还可在模型中单独配置，如：</p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp; //在模型里单独设置数据库连接信息</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; namespace Home\\Model;</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; use Think\\Model;</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; class UserModel extends Model{</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; protected $connection = array(</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &#39;db_type&#39; =&gt; &#39;mysql&#39;,</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &#39;db_user&#39; =&gt; &#39;root&#39;,</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &#39;db_pwd&#39; =&gt; &#39;1234&#39;,</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &#39;db_host&#39; =&gt; &#39;localhost&#39;,</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &#39;db_port&#39; =&gt; &#39;3306&#39;,</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &#39;db_name&#39; =&gt; &#39;thinkphp&#39;,</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &#39;db_charset&#39; =&gt; &#39;utf8&#39;,</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; );</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; }</span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">但是这样要是成功了也就好了，可是在运行程序的时候，还是提示错误，说是没有数据库的配置，在github中参考了好多thinkphp3.2的项目代码，也是采取一样的设置，我很纳闷为什么我的就不行，之后又在tp官网中查了好多，终于找到许多有着同样问题的同仁了，原来，只要加上一句“</span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&#39;DB-TYPE&#39;=&gt;&#39;mysql&#39;或者其他的类型都可以，最后就搞定了，在3.12可以得东西到了3.2以后就不行了，看来两者还是有很大的差异啊，还得更加深入地学习啊</span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong style="color: rgb(255, 64, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></strong></span></p><p><br style="text-align: left;"/></p>', 6, 1, 1, '2015-04-20'),
(6, 'SunShine', 'thinkphp3.2验证码的验证问题', '<p>thinkphp3.12的验证码和thinkphp3.2以上版本的验证码验证问题有明显的差异，之前我还是按照3.1.2的模式来进行验证码的验证，也就是将post过来的值进行MD5</p><p>加密，然后和session[&#39;verify&#39;]进行对比，之后总是无法进行匹配，最后将$_SESSION[&#39;verify&#39;]进行打印，发现是空值，真是好奇怪。</p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp; 后来看了别人的代码。他们的做法是在Application/Admin/Common目录下建立一个function.php文件，然后写上验证码验证的函数，如下：</p><p>&nbsp; function check_verify($code, $id = 1){</p><p><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>$verify = new \\Think\\Verify();</p><p><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>return $verify-&gt;check($code, $id);</p><p>&nbsp; }</p><p>然后在控制器下直接进行使用就行，如下：</p><p>$verify = I(&#39;verify&#39;);</p><p>if(!check_verify($verify)){</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $this-&gt;error(&#39;验证码输入错误！&#39;);</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }</p><p><br/></p><p>但是这样做的话始终得不到正确结果，也就是无论验证码输入的是正确的还是错误的，他都会显示错误，这也是thinkphp官网上登陆页面提交验证码的时候无论是正确还是错误，他都是跳转提示验证码错误。从github中fork的代码也是犯了和官网一样的错误，我也是醉了，真是坑爹啊，至于为什么在dump$_SESSION[&#39;verify&#39;]值为空，原因看了官网的一片文章才知道，</p><p><span style="color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &#39;Century Gothic&#39;, &#39;Microsoft yahei&#39;; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">关于session里面到底有没有值，是有的，在wamp/tmp下的就是，打开里面有verify_code,和verify_time,我最开始也注意到了，但不明白为什么提取不出来。</span><br style="color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &#39;Century Gothic&#39;, &#39;Microsoft yahei&#39;; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><span style="color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &#39;Century Gothic&#39;, &#39;Microsoft yahei&#39;; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">但是在tp3.2.3的THINKPHP/Library/Think/Verify下的verify.class.php它写的验证方法里确实是调用了这个verify_code来和人输入的验证码进行比对,大家可以去查证一下。</span><br style="color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &#39;Century Gothic&#39;, &#39;Microsoft yahei&#39;; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><span style="color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &#39;Century Gothic&#39;, &#39;Microsoft yahei&#39;; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">但为什么我们调不出来呢。我打$_SESSION[&#39;verify_code&#39;]是没有的。按网上一些朋友的解释可能是在3.2.3里如果弹到了新页面，这个验证码的session就会消失了。而变成新的session，比如视频后来的登录后redirect到Index/index后台管理页面去，session好像就变成了视频中主动手设的其他session值了。</span></p><p><font color="#323232" face="Century Gothic, Microsoft yahei"><span style="line-height: 28.7999992370605px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">最后的解决办法是什么呢，这更是坑爹啊，只是一个判断的条件不同，我更是醉了，有位老兄是这样写的，</span></font></p><p><font color="#323232" face="Century Gothic, Microsoft yahei"><span style="line-height: 28.7999992370605px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></font></p><ol class="linenums list-paddingleft-2" style="margin-left: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(43, 165, 216); white-space: normal; list-style-position: outside; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Consolas, &#39;Liberation Mono&#39;, Courier, monospace, 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><li><p><span class="pln" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">$code</span><span class="pun" style="color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">=</span><span class="pln" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;I</span><span class="pun" style="color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="str" style="color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">&#39;post.code&#39;</span><span class="pun" style="color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">);</span></p></li><li><p><span class="pln" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="kwd" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">if</span><span class="pun" style="color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="pln" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">check_code</span><span class="pun" style="color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="pln" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">$code</span><span class="pun" style="color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">)</span><span class="pln" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</span><span class="pun" style="color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">===</span><span class="pln" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</span><span class="kwd" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 136);">false</span><span class="pun" style="color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">){</span></p></li><li><p><span class="pln" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this</span><span class="pun" style="color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">-&gt;</span><span class="pln" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">error</span><span class="pun" style="color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">(</span><span class="str" style="color: rgb(0, 136, 0);">&#39;验证码错误&#39;</span><span class="pun" style="color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">);</span></p></li><li><p><span class="pln" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="pun" style="color: rgb(102, 102, 0);">}</span></p></li></ol><p>结果就正确了，我只能呵呵了，但是这个===还是很有学问的不是吗？</p><p><br/></p>', 6, 1, 1, '2015-04-21'),
(8, 'SunShine', 'thinkphp3.2的分页管理(转载）', '<p style="font-size: 13.3333330154419px; margin: 10px auto; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); font-family: verdana, Arial, helvetica, sans-seriff; line-height: 13px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">首先要搞清楚的就是ThinkPHP3.2.3的分页类已经被移到了Think\\Page.class.php,这是跟以前的版本有些不一样的，使用起来还是跟以前版本差不多，但是默认的效果不敢恭维，所以最好是自己加些样式。</p><p style="font-size: 13.3333330154419px; margin: 10px auto; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); font-family: verdana, Arial, helvetica, sans-seriff; line-height: 13px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">我加了一些样式(不怎么好看)，大家可以自行的再去改进分页样式，效果图：</p><p style="font-size: 13.3333330154419px; margin: 10px auto; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); font-family: verdana, Arial, helvetica, sans-seriff; line-height: 13px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></p><p style="font-size: 13.3333330154419px; margin: 10px auto; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); font-family: verdana, Arial, helvetica, sans-seriff; line-height: 13px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">在这里我有先把page的设置做成了一个函数getpage，将这个方法放到Application\\Common\\Common\\function.php(注意function不是类)中方便其他地方调用，代码如下：</p><p><span class="cnblogs_code_copy" style="padding-right: 5px; line-height: 1.5 !important;"><a title="复制代码" style="border: none !important;"><img src="/upload/image/20150423/1429794884950313.gif" alt="复制代码" style="border: none !important;"/></a></span></p><pre style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: &#39;Courier New&#39; !important;">&lt;?php/**\r\n&nbsp;*&nbsp;TODO&nbsp;基础分页的相同代码封装，使前台的代码更少\r\n&nbsp;*&nbsp;@param&nbsp;$count&nbsp;要分页的总记录数\r\n&nbsp;*&nbsp;@param&nbsp;int&nbsp;$pagesize&nbsp;每页查询条数\r\n&nbsp;*&nbsp;@return&nbsp;\\Think\\Page&nbsp;*/function&nbsp;getpage($count,&nbsp;$pagesize&nbsp;=&nbsp;10)&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$p&nbsp;=&nbsp;new&nbsp;Think\\Page($count,&nbsp;$pagesize);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$p-&gt;setConfig(&#39;header&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;&lt;li&nbsp;class=&quot;rows&quot;&gt;共&lt;b&gt;%TOTAL_ROW%&lt;/b&gt;条记录&amp;nbsp;第&lt;b&gt;%NOW_PAGE%&lt;/b&gt;页/共&lt;b&gt;%TOTAL_PAGE%&lt;/b&gt;页&lt;/li&gt;&#39;);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$p-&gt;setConfig(&#39;prev&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;上一页&#39;);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$p-&gt;setConfig(&#39;next&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;下一页&#39;);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$p-&gt;setConfig(&#39;last&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;末页&#39;);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$p-&gt;setConfig(&#39;first&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;首页&#39;);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$p-&gt;setConfig(&#39;theme&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;%FIRST%%UP_PAGE%%LINK_PAGE%%DOWN_PAGE%%END%%HEADER%&#39;);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$p-&gt;lastSuffix&nbsp;=&nbsp;false;//最后一页不显示为总页数\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;$p;\r\n}?&gt;</pre><p><span class="cnblogs_code_copy" style="padding-right: 5px; line-height: 1.5 !important;"><a title="复制代码" style="border: none !important;"><img src="/upload/image/20150423/1429794884950313.gif" alt="复制代码" style="border: none !important;"/></a></span></p><p style="font-size: 13.3333330154419px; margin: 10px auto; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); font-family: verdana, Arial, helvetica, sans-seriff; line-height: 13px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</p><p style="font-size: 13.3333330154419px; margin: 10px auto; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); font-family: verdana, Arial, helvetica, sans-seriff; line-height: 13px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">控制器中使用的代码如下：</p><p><span class="cnblogs_code_copy" style="padding-right: 5px; line-height: 1.5 !important;"><a title="复制代码" style="border: none !important;"><img src="/upload/image/20150423/1429794884950313.gif" alt="复制代码" style="border: none !important;"/></a></span></p><pre style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: &#39;Courier New&#39; !important;">public&nbsp;function&nbsp;showAllUsers()&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$m&nbsp;=&nbsp;M(&#39;User&#39;);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$where&nbsp;=&nbsp;&quot;id&gt;10&quot;;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$count&nbsp;=&nbsp;$m-&gt;where($where)-&gt;count();&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$p&nbsp;=&nbsp;getpage($count,1);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$list&nbsp;=&nbsp;$m-&gt;field(true)-&gt;where($where)-&gt;order(&#39;id&#39;)-&gt;limit($p-&gt;firstRow,&nbsp;$p-&gt;listRows)-&gt;select();&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;assign(&#39;select&#39;,&nbsp;$list);&nbsp;//&nbsp;赋值数据集\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;assign(&#39;page&#39;,&nbsp;$p-&gt;show());&nbsp;//&nbsp;赋值分页输出\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$this-&gt;display();\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}</pre><p><span class="cnblogs_code_copy" style="padding-right: 5px; line-height: 1.5 !important;"><a title="复制代码" style="border: none !important;"><img src="/upload/image/20150423/1429794884950313.gif" alt="复制代码" style="border: none !important;"/></a></span></p><p style="font-size: 13.3333330154419px; margin: 10px auto; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); font-family: verdana, Arial, helvetica, sans-seriff; line-height: 13px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</p><p style="font-size: 13.3333330154419px; margin: 10px auto; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); font-family: verdana, Arial, helvetica, sans-seriff; line-height: 13px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">接下来在View中的使用：</p><p><span class="cnblogs_code_copy" style="padding-right: 5px; line-height: 1.5 !important;"><a title="复制代码" style="border: none !important;"><img src="/upload/image/20150423/1429794884950313.gif" alt="复制代码" style="border: none !important;"/></a></span></p><pre style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: &#39;Courier New&#39; !important;">&lt;!DOCTYPE&nbsp;html&nbsp;PUBLIC&nbsp;&quot;-//W3C//DTD&nbsp;XHTML&nbsp;1.0&nbsp;Transitional//EN&quot;&nbsp;&quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd&quot;&gt;&lt;html&nbsp;xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;head&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;meta&nbsp;http-equiv=&quot;Content-Type&quot;&nbsp;content=&quot;text/html;&nbsp;charset=utf-8&quot;&nbsp;/&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;title&gt;用户信息输出&lt;/title&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;link&nbsp;href=&quot;__ROOT__/Public/Css/style.css&quot;&nbsp;rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot;&nbsp;type=&quot;text/css&quot;&nbsp;/&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;link&nbsp;href=&quot;__ROOT__/Public/Css/mypage.css&quot;&nbsp;rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot;&nbsp;type=&quot;text/css&quot;/&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;/head&gt;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;body&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;table&nbsp;width=&quot;405&quot;&nbsp;border=&quot;1&quot;&nbsp;cellpadding=&quot;1&quot;&nbsp;cellspacing=&quot;1&quot;&nbsp;bgcolor=&quot;#99CC33&quot;&nbsp;bordercolor=&quot;#FFFFFF&quot;&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;tr&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;td&nbsp;colspan=&quot;3&quot;&nbsp;bgcolor=&quot;#FFFFFF&quot;&nbsp;class=&quot;title&quot;&nbsp;align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;当前登录用户：{$Think.session.admin}&lt;/td&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;tr&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;td&nbsp;colspan=&quot;3&quot;&nbsp;bgcolor=&quot;#FFFFFF&quot;&nbsp;class=&quot;title&quot;&nbsp;align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;用户信息&lt;/td&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;tr&nbsp;class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;td&nbsp;bgcolor=&quot;#FFFFFF&quot;&nbsp;width=&quot;44&quot;&gt;ID&lt;/td&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;td&nbsp;bgcolor=&quot;#FFFFFF&quot;&nbsp;width=&quot;120&quot;&gt;用户名&lt;/td&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;td&nbsp;bgcolor=&quot;#FFFFFF&quot;&nbsp;width=&quot;223&quot;&gt;密码&lt;/td&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;foreach&nbsp;name=&#39;select&#39;&nbsp;item=&#39;user&#39;&nbsp;&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;tr&nbsp;class=&quot;content&quot;&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;td&nbsp;bgcolor=&quot;#FFFFFF&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;{$user.id}&lt;/td&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;td&nbsp;bgcolor=&quot;#FFFFFF&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;{$user.account}&lt;/td&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;td&nbsp;bgcolor=&quot;#FFFFFF&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;{$user.pwd}&lt;/td&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;/foreach&gt;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;tr&nbsp;class=&quot;content&quot;&gt;\r\n